Kuwaiti Armed Forces (KAF): Kuwaiti Land Forces (KLF), Kuwaiti
Navy, Kuwaiti Air Force (Al-Quwwat al-Jawwiya al-Kuwaitiya;
includes Kuwaiti Air Defense Force, KADF), 25th Commando Brigade,
and the Kuwait Emiri Guard Brigade; Kuwaiti National Guard (KNG);
Coast Guard (Ministry of Interior) (2022)
theKuwaitthe Kuwaiti National Guard reports directly to the prime minister and the amir and possesses an independent command structure, equipment inventory, and logistics corps separate from the Ministry of Defense, the regular armed services, and the Ministry of Interior; it is responsible for protecting critical infrastructure and providing support for the Ministries of Interior and Defense as required
